nce: A Personal View of the Search for God\u200b<\/a><span class=\"redactor-invisible-space\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.amazon.com\/gp\/product\/0143112627\/ref=as_li_qf_asin_il_tl?ie=UTF8&amp;tag=jamesclearema-20&amp;creative=9325&amp;linkCode=as2&amp;creativeASIN=0143112627&amp;linkId=a76704bb251dc2550d9f92c0f105fca0\">\u200b<\/a><\/span><\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-css-opacity\"\/>\n\n\n\n<p>II.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>The poet and Pulitzer Prize winner&nbsp;<strong data-redactor-tag=\"strong\">Mary Oliver<\/strong>&nbsp;with some suggestions for your one precious life:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>&#8220;Instructions for living a life: Pay attention. Be astonished. Tell about it.&#8221;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><em data-redactor-tag=\"em\">Source:&nbsp;<a href=\"https:\/\/www.amazon.com\/gp\/product\/0807068934\/ref=as_li_qf_asin_il_tl?ie=UTF8&amp;tag=jamesclearema-20&amp;creative=9325&amp;linkCode=as2&amp;creativeASIN=0807068934&amp;linkId=972ee78fccca92fc048196936d36247c\">Red Bird<\/a><\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"h-1-question-for-you\">1 QUESTION FOR YOU<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>What would 10-year-old me say? What would 80-year-old me say?<\/p>\n\n\n\n\n\n<p>Until next week,<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>James Clear<br><em data-redactor-tag=\"em\">Author of the million-copy bestseller,&nbsp;<a href=\"https:\/\/atomichabits.com\/\" data-cke-saved-href=\"https:\/\/atomichabits.com\">Atomic Habits<\/a><br><\/em><em data-redactor-tag=\"em\">Creator of&nbsp;<a href=\"https:\/\/habitsacademy.com\/\" data-cke-saved-href=\"https:\/\/habitsacademy.com\/\">The Habits Academy<\/a>&nbsp;and the&nbsp;<a href=\"https:\/\/jamesclear.com\/habit-journal\" data-cke-saved-href=\"https:\/\/jamesclear.com\/habit-journal\">Habit Journal<\/a><\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>P.S.\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/jamesclear.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/10\/not-in-this-grocery.png\">Not in this grocery store<\/a>.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>3 IDEAS FROM ME I. &#8220;Aim to be great in 10 years. Build health h